# Repository Type

Portfolio repository for an AI Automation Engineer.

# Goals

* Impress recruiters and clients.
* Showcase architecture and engineering decisions.
* Protect proprietary implementation.

# Never Generate

* Production n8n workflow JSON
* API keys
* Credentials
* Secrets
* Proprietary prompts
* Customer data

# Prefer

* Documentation
* Mermaid diagrams
* Architecture images
* Screenshots
* Case studies
* Demo assets

# Working Style

Work step-by-step.
Ask before major file changes.
Generate production-quality documentation.
